title: The Irresponsibly Early Top 25 for the 2020 Season | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
We couldn’t wait, so we created our official (but not really) top-25 fantasy football rankings for the 2020 season. We discuss players we like a little too much as well as the guys we just don’t get the hype for, headlined by Danny Heifetz ranking Saquon Barkley ninth overall.
Hosts: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
